PN,44401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA police search adviser believed there
OL,8,Fwas a 5% possibility that Noah Donohoe
OL,9,Fwas in the culvert in which his body
OL,10,Fwas eventually found, an inquest has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FSergeant Hutchings, who was the lead
OL,14,FPolsa (police search adviser) in the
OL,15,Fsearch for the 14-year-old in 2020,
OL,16,Fsaid there had been no evidence to
OL,17,Fsuggest the schoolboy had entered the
OL,18,Funderground water tunnel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe inquest into the death of Noah at
OL,8,FBelfast Coroner's Court, which is
OL,9,Fbeing heard with a jury, is now in its
OL,10,Fsixth week.
OL,12,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,13,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,14,Fin the storm drain tunnel in north
OL,15,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,16,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,17,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,18,Fcity.
OL,20,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,21,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FUnder questioning from Brenda Campbell
OL,8,FKC on Thursday, Mr Hutchings said he
OL,9,Fwould have discussed the stream and
OL,10,Fpipe in a handover from a colleague
OL,11,Fwhen he resumed duty on Tuesday ` two
OL,12,Fdays after Noah was last seen.
OL,14,FAt this point, the search was focused
OL,15,Faround Noah's last sighting in the
OL,16,Farea around Northwood Road and
OL,17,FNorthwood Linear Park, where the
OL,18,Fculvert was located.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Hutchings said his colleague could
OL,8,Fnot have commenced searching the pipe
OL,9,Fovernight as the confined spaces team
OL,10,Fwould not have been on.
OL,12,FHe said the pipe did not need
OL,13,Fsearching "immediately" because they
OL,14,Fdid "not expect him to be in there",
OL,15,Fadding there was "nothing to suggest"
OL,16,Fhe had entered the culvert.
OL,18,FHe said he assigned a team to examine
OL,19,Fit but he had "more important things
OL,20,Fto do" in searching areas where Noah
OL,21,F"was more likely to be".
OL,26,@uD@KOUuD@WO]vD@EOUvD@cO]wD@ROUwD@eO]{D@
OL,26,AOOU|D@FO]}D@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell, representing Noah's
OL,8,Fmother Fiona, asked whether it was a
OL,9,Fpossibility that he was in the pipe.
OL,11,FMr Hutchings replied: "It proved it
OL,12,Fwas a possibility but at the time we
OL,13,Fdid not expect him to go into that
OL,14,Fpipe."
OL,16,FHe told the barrister he had not ask
OL,17,Fhis colleague how close he got to the
OL,18,Fpipe but he had not been told he had
OL,19,Fheard screams.
OL,26,@sD@WOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAsked about earlier evidence in which
OL,8,Fa Community Rescue Search member said
OL,9,Fthey were operating on a "50-50
OL,10,Fstrategy" about whether the boy was
OL,11,Funder or above ground, Mr Hutchings
OL,12,Fsaid his assessment on the boy being
OL,13,Fin the pipe was nowhere near that
OL,14,Fratio.
OL,16,FHe said it was "5%, even if that" and
OL,17,Fthe search of the pipe was to content
OL,18,Fhimself that "he was not there".
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@IO]xD@POUxD@aO]zD@NOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said the 5% figure did not
OL,8,Finfluence the speed or urgency of the
OL,9,Fsearch of the culvert.
OL,11,FThe jury heard it was the working
OL,12,Fhypothesis that Noah was missing
OL,13,Fvoluntarily, although concerns about
OL,14,Fhis worrying behaviour had been noted
OL,15,Fafter reports that he was naked
OL,16,Findicated the possible "disturbed
OL,17,Fstate of mind" which "may point to the
OL,18,Fpresence of some drug".
OL,20,FMr Hutchings said it was taken as a
OL,21,Fpossible explanation for his behaviour.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@NO]yD@VOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FUnder questioning, he also said he was
OL,8,Faware members of the public near
OL,9,FNorthwood Linear Park had heard
OL,10,Fpossible signs of distress and screams
OL,11,Fthrough the night.
OL,13,FAsked to explain the 5% probability
OL,14,Ffor the culvert in light of this
OL,15,Finformation, Mr Hutchings said it was
OL,16,Fsearched "as quickly as possible"
OL,17,Fwhile "other high priority areas" were
OL,18,Fsearched.
OL,26,@xD@JOUxD@aO]yD@GOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said they could have searched the
OL,8,Fwhole pipe and found he was not in
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,FMr Hutchings said he "got the result"
OL,12,Fof finding Noah without anyone else
OL,13,Fbeing injured in the search.
OL,15,FMs Campbell put it to him that his
OL,16,Ftask was preferably to find the boy
OL,17,Falive.
OL,19,FHe said: "I would've done anything to
OL,20,Ffind him alive ` unfortunately he was
OL,21,Fdead."
OL,26,@sD@VOUsD@eO]{D@JOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said at "no point" was the search
OL,8,Fof the pipe a rescue mission.
OL,10,FAsked about the outlet of the culvert
OL,11,Ftowards Belfast Harbour, he said: "I
OL,12,Fwould have been wasting the limited
OL,13,Fresources I had at that time by
OL,14,Fsending them down to the Lough."
OL,16,FHe said he did not consider calling
OL,17,Fdivers or other specialist personnel
OL,18,Fas the WICS (working in confined
OL,19,Fspaces) team was going through the
OL,20,Fculvert methodically.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@UO]sD@cOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Hutchings later ordered a drone to
OL,8,Fbe flown over the outlet on Thursday
OL,9,Fto "discount" that Noah may have
OL,10,Fcrawled all the way through and "could
OL,11,Fbe lying there".
OL,13,FElsewhere on that day, he said he
OL,14,Fbecame aware the search of the pipe
OL,15,Fhad slowed down due to difficult
OL,16,Fconditions.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@MO]rD@aOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Hutchings was also asked about a
OL,8,Fnote in his logs that the senior
OL,9,Finvestigating officer was working
OL,10,Funder a scenario that Noah was missing
OL,11,Fvoluntarily or under the influence of
OL,12,Fa third party.
OL,14,FHe said the "main one" was voluntarily
OL,15,Fbut they still had to consider he
OL,16,Fcould be in somebody's car or home.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe jury heard that between the
OL,8,FTuesday morning, when 180 metres had
OL,9,Fbeen searched, teams had advanced a
OL,10,Ffurther 320 metres within the 970-
OL,11,Fmetre storm drain by Friday morning.
OL,13,FThe remainder of the pipe was said to
OL,14,Fbe half-filled with water, at low tide.
OL,16,FHe said he was then "grasping at
OL,17,Fstraws" for anyone that could help.
OL,26,@xD@UOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA PSNI search-and-rescue team with
OL,8,Fcaving experience put on drysuits and
OL,9,Fsearched the pipe on Saturday and
OL,10,Ffound Noah's body.
OL,12,FMr Hutchings said he has since learned
OL,13,Fthat, under health and safety rules,
OL,14,Fthey should not have been going in
OL,15,Fthere without confined space training.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell suggested 10 possible
OL,8,Ffailures in the search process,
OL,9,Fincluding an alleged failure to
OL,10,Fprioritise the culvert as an area the
OL,11,Fboy may be, an alleged delay in
OL,12,Fseeking maps or information of the
OL,13,Fhazards within, and an alleged failure
OL,14,Fto treat the operation as a rescue
OL,15,Fmission.
OL,17,FMr Hutchings said he did not accept
OL,18,Fany of Ms Campbell's points and said
OL,19,Fhe stood by his assertion that nothing
OL,20,Fthe team could have done differently
OL,21,Fcould have found Noah any sooner.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FUnder further questioning by Donal
OL,8,FLunny KC, who represents the PSNI, Mr
OL,9,FHutchings said he had never written
OL,10,Fdown "5%" during the search and said
OL,11,Fhe gave the figure in the "spur of the
OL,12,Fmoment" when asked by Ms Campbell.
OL,14,FHowever, he said he considered the
OL,15,Funderground system a "far lower
OL,16,Fprobability" than other areas.
OL,18,FHe said he had ongoing training since
OL,19,Fbecoming a Polsa in 2007 ` and had
OL,20,Fconducted more than 100 searches in
OL,21,Fthe last year.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@IO]sD@[OUtD@GO]wD@VOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIt also heard that 50% of missing
OL,8,Fpersons in Noah's age range are found
OL,9,Fwithin three kilometres of their home
OL,10,Fwhile males tend to hang around
OL,11,Fstreets and are traced quicker by
OL,12,Fgeneral police patrols.
OL,14,FMr Hutchings explained the rationale
OL,15,Ffor the search area through references
OL,16,Fto mobile phone pings, Noah's recent
OL,17,Fsearch history and CCTV sightings.
OL,19,FHe said densely-populated urban areas
OL,20,Fcan be much more difficult to search
OL,21,Fthan open areas.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAsked about how a search from the
OL,8,Fother end of the culvert would have
OL,9,Flined up with standard practice, he
OL,10,Fsaid: "You don't do it. You stay at
OL,11,Fthe place last seen and work
OL,12,Fsystematically out.
OL,14,F"Me jumping away to the far side could
OL,15,Fhave missed him completely."
OL,17,FMr Hutchings also said search teams
OL,18,Fnever heard a response to any call-out
OL,19,For human sounds within the pipe that
OL,20,Fdid not come from the team itself.
OL,26,@rD@GOUvD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772745127
OL,3,CPolice search team lead gave 5% chance
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe was in culvert, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said if they had heard such sounds,
OL,8,Fthey would have initiated a rescue
OL,9,Foperation.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the coroner Mr Justice
OL,12,FRooney told the jury he would update
OL,13,Fthem on the progress of the inquest,
OL,14,Fwhich he said was "moving, maybe, not
OL,15,Fas quickly as I would have hoped".
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@aO]
